{"tid":1550461,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你有冇諗過自己行動既動機同目的","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T09:57:54.000Z","uid":31974,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3c88554313fcab113440db1a2a4c9ef8bdc81d72","tid":1550461,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"已經幾百個post分析過<br />\n唔好再打陣地戰<br />\n唔好再圍狗屋<br />\n唔好再同狗對峙<br />\n<br />\n但係每次行動個規律係點<br />\n我唔講你自己都知<br />\n<br />\n唔該<br />\n每個人自己獨立思考下<br />\n你企係個場度到底想達成啲咩<br />\n達成左既話 你想離開定有新作務要做<br />\n未達成既 留低繼續定另覓其他方法<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">除非你目的係入新屋嶺<br />\n如果唔係 我諗唔到有咩理由你一定要等俾狗推先散水</span>"},{"pid":"eb5e05281fc70165a0ecf3335c096066ad7f91e8","tid":1550461,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:11:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74da9f8eb04860353d46eb23742398ffa86e7918","tid":1550461,"uid":194601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"5359ce48592036d28deb47a7b7b374cbd16a9ba6","tid":1550461,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a17f22f620fbb2cc35cb9daf77eb09800086699a","tid":1550461,"uid":244781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"大家行動前真係要諗清楚，唔好再送頭，唔想再見到巴打流血，就算流都要流得有意義"},{"pid":"f895842ab2589734a5f7c66a3ef14a45b05e1c35","tid":1550461,"uid":103159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"屌哂你班偽前線<br />\n成班mk 仔女咁得把聲"},{"pid":"9fffd8381c41d24bf294242bf3f8caa7d2f70951","tid":1550461,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:17:37.000Z","msg":"留名睇有人話<br />\n兄弟爬山，要信任前線"},{"pid":"cd23b417d7c72626d519a2c729272b80b8487e24","tid":1550461,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>九月八，遮打見！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZUq8PfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUq8PfJ.png&h=6ed8457a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外以下口號可以一記：<br />\n-Free Hong Kong, Democracy now!<br />\n-Fight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong!<br />\n-Five Demands, Not one less!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">練定美國國歌一齊唱K</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=a9e62175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a>"},{"pid":"ed5e29f3c7a08376e4e088dbed03b1e0bae2fd17","tid":1550461,"uid":31974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"要塞路 燒野 爆閘<br />\n做乜都好<br />\n你做完咪散<br />\n點解一定要成班企係等狗出<br />\n你為乜先？<br />\n撚狗緊要定手足緊要？<br />\n二百萬你估好多？<br />\n<br />\n你地對住班殺人犯唱歌仔 叫口號<br />\n佢地係唔會hurt架<br />\n<br />\n唔該 諗返我地既初衷啦<br />\n點解我地要出黎呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">係五大訴求呀</span>"},{"pid":"5155b827769d5b07537236b4c04ad6410e97e27e","tid":1550461,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:22:45.000Z","msg":"要 有獨立 思考<br />\n<br />\n不圍加屋，不打地戰，不被捕"},{"pid":"0d68952c32081eedcedbb6e710825a5cfb682e7a","tid":1550461,"uid":286685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:24:48.000Z","msg":"不圍加屋，不打地戰，不被捕"},{"pid":"a0399d1c20535a80547d4392ba45da826b891163","tid":1550461,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有集會開始前，應先唱頌或奏《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n參加者應當起立，肅立致敬<br />\n右手置於心胸前<br />\n任何非宗教的頭飾應摘除並放置於左肩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQQpnEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQQpnEV.png&h=d7a5b483&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ae44c126fae61a6b1d079be1ecaf86caecf127a","tid":1550461,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec30cdd9c78ed0ab9260c9c9a608af040a82b452","tid":1550461,"uid":271617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家唔好再糾纏太子站有冇死人，警狗有冇強姦人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家覺唔覺近1星期好多 post 都係冇任何證據得張 whatsapp 對話圖，下面D人就開始話希望炒車。其他有曬證據同影片嘅 721 831卧底開槍，同之後活動就冇咩人討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再糾纏係太子站有冇死人，點解？<br />\n1. 欠缺實質證據，除非有人認識死者人士行出黎。<br />\n2. 黑警殺完人屍體都一定運去中國啦，唔會留係香港 (相比中國，香港更易被發現)<br />\n3. 就算去圍狗鐵狗屋都一定唔會比到CCTV你<br />\n4. 81歲浮屍都話可疑 (甚至過千正評)，轉移視線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 太多 fake news (警狗強姦... 得張圖冇其實任何證據)，大量資訊轟炸，造成資訊疲勞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">嚴重分散咗其他核彈，甚至整個活動焦點</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「我地都要贏依場仗 先可以全力清算到黑警同政府 輸咗嘅話真相永遠石沉大海 只會清算返我地手足」</span><br />\n<br />\n我地係要贏呀 依家文宣人數 勇武人數都需要增加 雨革就係咁樣而輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=1de42daa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"c980a3d9652b96bf4b87fb3cd20a877f69722d84","tid":1550461,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:32:29.000Z","msg":"不圍加屋，不打地戰，不被捕"},{"pid":"93e8a675c9cc88b24462aeca915013fc4de77640","tid":1550461,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:33:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\">【轉發】已退役前英國皇家海軍叫大家思考一個盲點<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536560</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n[兩日遇到一個已退役前英國皇家海軍，佢接受過防暴訓練，想叫我代佢叫大家認真思考一下呢一個盲點，我代佢列出重點。<br />\n<br />\n1. 圍狗屋目的？<br />\n<br />\n是想引防暴出黎身水身汗?<br />\n<br />\n定抑或心理作用，因為次次都輸，想贏番一次?<br />\n<br />\n2. 圍狗屋正中狗仔下懷<br />\n<br />\n狗仔匿曬入屋，<br />\n<br />\n大家冇辦法睇到佢哋嘅數量、裝備、動靜。"},{"pid":"3b5a0f8c84e24321982a0dc4eec0bb99c6ef7405","tid":1550461,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"51bba0117295bf83dc702c1e66b87f07c85b620c","tid":1550461,"uid":8600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a717dbe9592e51bb33f63f6d8667df19b42d17","tid":1550461,"uid":242323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"成日等班仆街擺曬陣先攻<br />\n有咩用⋯⋯<br />\n希望前線會改進<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"7d8464e6663b8883b02c02c18f6d5502c182d39d","tid":1550461,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"最重要嘅係警覺性呀<br />\n不論前中後都好<br />\n落到場都要保持警惕<br />\n現場每分每秒都係變緊<br />\n琴日太子一退 差d人踩人"},{"pid":"0d1831af83b8da475d7f741966a75ca47f08d06a","tid":1550461,"uid":34239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:54:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cf1f76827a5fea4cacabfb5bf02f6e4dbb2bd00","tid":1550461,"uid":57771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"個人行動動機: 唔俾手足落單 工具人 幫得幾多得幾多 唔想做民主運動既free rider"},{"pid":"e942c335f08785c2ae20f5a66722035219c913cf","tid":1550461,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"其實你又有冇諗過依家唔係打機 ? <br />\n<br />\n無大台既最大缺點就係好難令成千上萬既人做到同一個動作 / 方向 <br />\n而依個情況撐左 3 個月<br />\n大方向大家都做到<br />\n但一到啲細節位 就完全做唔到"},{"pid":"c99f6152cb0ef1ddff0ca5b5278fe9d5901b5ca6","tid":1550461,"uid":77102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"不被捕，不受傷呀咁多位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要記住其他手足見到會好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539472ba448d6005678558de2823ec603d0eb90a","tid":1550461,"uid":262796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"認真 <br />\n企過前線都會明白嗰時係會有種高揚感 會令到個人好high 所以當有狗 你唔 逃走而留喺度打狗我會好明白你嘅感受<br />\n<br />\n但係當你哋做曬要做嘅嘢 而前面係冇狗嘅時候 真係唔好成支竹咁留喺嗰度 而係要諗下 狗出嚟之後係點 你走會點 唔走又點<br />\n<br />\n老實講喺前線打得嘅真係佔好少好少 你要一下喺嗰度團結曬後面嗰班冇諗過打嘅去打交 真係難過登天 <br />\n所以 各位巴打絲打 留喺前線嗰陣時真係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">諗清楚諗清楚諗清楚</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}